向啲）<br />\n都冇大問題<br />\n好似天空上面有一片烏雲<br />\n唔會落雨令你淋濕<br />\n都唔會咁易俾你見到陽光<br />\n但你仍然可以如常生活"},{"pid":"4b468e771117478823328dc88749b419e68a7b14","tid":974144,"uid":191919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fee5e851bf9143c7226b2bf28d09b3b79d1e1e1","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"有好多野自己覺得好刻骨銘心 念念不忘<br />\n講出黎完來好普通 好平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426fd32b37f5b421b3ac8adb10d5ee71a5adff70","tid":974144,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30aa8394ea3bd6013c94a3f4f42bcc0804853063","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b70087f4ba6a7b786d24a7f766d4429246d522","tid":974144,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"個女仔呢段日子有冇拍拖?<br />\n<br />\n係咪已經係人o地o既女人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"有 好多仔添 佢依家個男朋友都叫拍咗幾年<br />\n都幾穩定下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"巴打見到佢同佢男友一齊，或者見到佢地啲sweet sweet合照，會唔會好痛好絕望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會想有朝一日佢地散咗，你就可以同佢一齊？定會想佢幸幸福福，一直落去唔好散？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e918fb764ce1560a7eb530082cc81233b328a07f","tid":974144,"uid":2673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"依家仲係喺佢身邊等緊機會？<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過set個限期畀自己？"},{"pid":"90beb191b4319a4f41ff5f50a1d7560712874e5d","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e918fb764ce1560a7eb530082cc81233b328a07f","tid":974144,"uid":2673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:32:35.000Z","msg":"依家仲係喺佢身邊等緊機會？<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過set個限期畀自己？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"自問都冇機會了<br />\n我諗到我真正放低佢之後先會開始另一段關係<br />\n又或者等我遇到另一個我真心鍾意嘅人囉<br />\n'I know you can see I'm incredibly blue<br />\nBut I'm not that lonely yet'"},{"pid":"10502c49a9f54f39ba24e61a07ebb26fa4ad42f6","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"426fd32b37f5b421b3ac8adb10d5ee71a5adff70","tid":974144,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30aa8394ea3bd6013c94a3f4f42bcc0804853063","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b70087f4ba6a7b786d24a7f766d4429246d522","tid":974144,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"個女仔呢段日子有冇拍拖?<br />\n<br />\n係咪已經係人o地o既女人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"有 好多仔添 佢依家個男朋友都叫拍咗幾年<br />\n都幾穩定下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"巴打見到佢同佢男友一齊，或者見到佢地啲sweet sweet合照，會唔會好痛好絕望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會想有朝一日佢地散咗，你就可以同佢一齊？定會想佢幸幸福福，一直落去唔好散？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:52:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔係好用social Media<br />\n佢現任我一次都冇見過<br />\n其實大家近年都好少聯絡<br />\n<br />\n大學曾經有一排有啲好瘋狂嘅諗法<br />\n好想佢有咩意外 有啲困境<br />\n然後我可以係佢身邊幫佢 陪佢<br />\n有機會可以證明我自己<br />\n<br />\n每次都覺得自己好蠢 好自私<br />\n佢入咗大學之後都變咗好多<br />\n佢以前同我講過好多想做嘅嘢<br />\n我見到佢去緊自己啱嘅方向<br />\n行緊條啱佢自己嘅路<br />\n<br />\n我而家淨係想佢開開心心<br />\n呢個係我嘅first priority <br />\n至於我自己可以對生活compromise <br />\n我好希望佢幸福快樂"},{"pid":"470723da1f8c6492c456590ba1669855259d23cd","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T18:52:47.000Z","msg":"If I should stay I would only be in your way"},{"pid":"d950838dc16ea45431a0494abb31bcc7fee89420","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10502c49a9f54f39ba24e61a07ebb26fa4ad42f6","tid":974144,"uid":25126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"426fd32b37f5b421b3ac8adb10d5ee71a5adff70","tid":974144,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30aa8394ea3bd6013c94a3f4f42bcc0804